## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="0499f-874">O exemplo a seguir mostra como salvar um <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XElement> em um <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0499f-874">The following example shows how to save an <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XElement> to an <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();  
XmlWriterSettings xws = new XmlWriterSettings();  
xws.OmitXmlDeclaration = true;  
using (XmlWriter xw = XmlWriter.Create(sb, xws)) {  
    XElement root = new XElement("Root",  
        new XElement("Child", "child content")  
    );  
    root.Save(xw);  
}  
Console.WriteLine(sb.ToString());  
```  
  
```vb  
Dim sb As StringBuilder = New StringBuilder()  
Dim xws As XmlWriterSettings = New XmlWriterSettings()  
xws.OmitXmlDeclaration = True  
Using xw = XmlWriter.Create(sb, xws)  
    Dim root As XElement = <Root>  
                               <Child>child content</Child>  
                           </Root>  
    root.Save(xw)  
End Using  
Console.WriteLine(sb.ToString())  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0499f-875">Este exemplo gera a seguinte saída:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0499f-875">This example produces the following output:</span></span>  
  
```xml  
<Root><Child>child content</Child></Root>  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="0499f-919">Este método destina-se tornar mais fácil de manter uma lista de pares nome/valor como um conjunto de atributos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0499f-919">This method is designed to make it easy to maintain a list of name/value pairs as a set of attributes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0499f-920">Mantendo a lista, você precisará adicionar pares, pares de modificar ou excluir esses pares.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0499f-920">When maintaining the list, you need to add pairs, modify pairs, or delete pairs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0499f-921">Se você chamar esse método passando um nome que não existe como um atributo, este método cria um atributo para você.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0499f-921">If you call this method passing a name that does not exist as an attribute, this method creates an attribute for you.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0499f-922">Se você chamar esse método, passando o nome de um atributo existente, esse método modifica o valor do atributo para o valor especificado por você.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0499f-922">If you call this method passing the name of an existing attribute, this method modifies the value of the attribute to the value that you specify.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0499f-923">Se você passar `null` para `value`, esse método Remove o atributo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0499f-923">If you pass `null` for `value`, this method removes the attribute.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0499f-924">Esse método gerará o <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject.Changed> e o <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject.Changing> eventos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0499f-924">This method will raise the <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject.Changed> and the <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject.Changing> events.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0499f-925">O valor é atribuído ao atributo com o nome especificado.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0499f-925">The value is assigned to the attribute with the specified name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0499f-926">Se nenhum atributo com o nome especificado existir, um novo atributo é adicionado.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0499f-926">If no attribute with the specified name exists, a new attribute is added.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0499f-927">Se o valor for `null`, o atributo com o nome especificado, se houver, será excluído.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0499f-927">If the value is `null`, the attribute with the specified name, if any, is deleted.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0499f-928">Para obter mais informações, consulte [mantendo pares de nome/valor](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/fe9798bf-b5e2-4a3c-a86c-7f8638912691).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0499f-928">For more information, see [Maintaining Name/Value Pairs](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/fe9798bf-b5e2-4a3c-a86c-7f8638912691).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="0499f-929">O exemplo a seguir cria um elemento com um atributo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0499f-929">The following example creates an element with an attribute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0499f-930">Ele usa esse método para substituir o conteúdo do atributo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0499f-930">It then uses this method to replace the content of the attribute.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Create an element with no content.  
XElement root = new XElement("Root");  
  
// Add some name/value pairs.  
root.SetAttributeValue("Att1", 1);  
root.SetAttributeValue("Att2", 2);  
root.SetAttributeValue("Att3", 3);  
Console.WriteLine(root);  
  
// Modify one of the name/value pairs.  
root.SetAttributeValue("Att2", 22);  
Console.WriteLine(root);  
  
// Remove one of the name/value pairs.  
root.SetAttributeValue("Att3", null);  
Console.WriteLine(root);  
```  
  
```vb  
' Create an element with no content.  
Dim root As XElement = <Root/>  
  
' Add some name/value pairs.  
root.SetAttributeValue("Att1", 1)  
root.SetAttributeValue("Att2", 2)  
root.SetAttributeValue("Att3", 3)  
Console.WriteLine(root)  
  
' Modify one of the name/value pairs.  
root.SetAttributeValue("Att2", 22)  
Console.WriteLine(root)  
  
' Remove one of the name/value pairs.  
root.SetAttributeValue("Att3", Nothing)  
Console.WriteLine(root)  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0499f-931">Este exemplo gera a seguinte saída:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0499f-931">This example produces the following output:</span></span>  
  
```  
<Root Att1="1" Att2="2" Att3="3" />  
<Root Att1="1" Att2="22" Att3="3" />  
<Root Att1="1" Att2="22" />  
```
